BuildAtlas backend package metadata file.

This README exists so setuptools can resolve `project.readme` during editable
installs (`uv sync`) for the backend project.

## Machine Learning Extras

To install the optional ML dependencies (numpy, scikit-learn, torch), run:

```
pip install -e .[ml]
```

